1
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:34,320
=Hold a Court Now=

2
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:38,460
=Episode 13=

3
00:01:38,540 --> 00:01:41,240
(Police)

4
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:43,150
She wants to force
a confession out of me.

5
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:44,639
She's using Fei's safety

6
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:46,029
to break my spirit.

7
00:01:46,030 --> 00:01:47,159
But she would never

8
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:49,320
actually hurt Fei.

9
00:01:49,470 --> 00:01:51,189
That's why we have to stay calm.

10
00:01:51,190 --> 00:01:52,510
Don't panic.

11
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:54,680
Look,

12
00:01:55,030 --> 00:01:56,430
let me take you back.

13
00:01:56,880 --> 00:01:58,389
You need to get some rest.

14
00:01:58,390 --> 00:02:00,240
In case Fei comes back on her own,

15
00:02:00,470 --> 00:02:02,320
you should be home to look after her.

16
00:02:03,080 --> 00:02:05,320
I'll head back out to search.

17
00:02:17,910 --> 00:02:19,040
Shu Jing.

18
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:20,160
Shu Jing!

19
00:02:20,510 --> 00:02:22,160
What's wrong? Come on.

20
00:02:24,750 --> 00:02:25,879
Shu Jing?

21
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:26,799
Shu Jing?

22
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:29,840
(Qingcheng District People's Court,
Tianhai City)

23
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:32,480
Why isn't Le here yet?

24
00:02:34,510 --> 00:02:36,320
Le! Over here!

25
00:02:36,630 --> 00:02:37,670
Hurry!

26
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:41,670
Who's being so nice today?

27
00:02:41,880 --> 00:02:42,789
I got this for you.

28
00:02:42,790 --> 00:02:43,950
Thanks.

29
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:46,069
Look, I'm starving.
Let me grab a bite first,

30
00:02:46,070 --> 00:02:47,950
then I'll update everyone.

31
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,230
Take your time.

32
00:02:55,590 --> 00:02:56,910
I just got in touch

33
00:02:57,160 --> 00:02:58,589
with Mr. Lian.

34
00:02:58,590 --> 00:02:59,790
He said Ms. Shu

35
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:01,440
woke up once.

36
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:03,349
But she still has a fever,

37
00:03:03,350 --> 00:03:04,880
and she's very weak.

38
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,469
She insisted on going out to find Fei

39
00:03:06,470 --> 00:03:07,950
and ended up taking a fall.

40
00:03:08,030 --> 00:03:09,350
Is she okay?

41
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:11,909
She's fine.

42
00:03:11,910 --> 00:03:14,509
The doctor gave her a sedative,

43
00:03:14,510 --> 00:03:16,070
so she's asleep again.

44
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:18,110
What should we do then?

45
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,469
We were just saying

46
00:03:19,470 --> 00:03:21,239
we'd go see her after work.

47
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:23,350
But there are so many of us,

48
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:25,189
it might not be a good idea to go now.

49
00:03:25,190 --> 00:03:26,440
Don't go.

50
00:03:26,630 --> 00:03:28,279
If everyone crowds in there,

51
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,909
we'll just be standing around worrying

52
00:03:29,910 --> 00:03:31,390
without being able to help.

53
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:33,909
I'll go take care of her
for the next few days.

54
00:03:33,910 --> 00:03:35,509
If it gets to be too much,

55
00:03:35,510 --> 00:03:36,959
we can all pitch in

56
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,159
and take shifts later.

57
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:39,200
Alright.

58
00:03:39,470 --> 00:03:40,239
How about we all help

59
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,790
look for the kid after work?

60
00:03:42,310 --> 00:03:43,679
Tianhai is so big.

61
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,040
Where do we even start?

62
00:03:45,910 --> 00:03:46,959
I have an idea.

63
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,909
Everyone, reach out to your friends

64
00:03:48,910 --> 00:03:50,029
and relatives.

65
00:03:50,030 --> 00:03:51,069
Share Fei's info

66
00:03:51,070 --> 00:03:53,070
and spread the word.

67
00:03:53,470 --> 00:03:54,309
The police is better

68
00:03:54,310 --> 00:03:57,040
at searching for missing persons.

69
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:01,439
Or we could try
thinking outside the box.

70
00:04:01,440 --> 00:04:02,760
Besides the police

71
00:04:02,790 --> 00:04:04,469
and standard investigation methods,

72
00:04:04,470 --> 00:04:06,469
is there any other way
to get a breakthrough?

73
00:04:06,470 --> 00:04:08,350
They're just two girls.

74
00:04:08,590 --> 00:04:12,350
Is there a way of thinking
that differs from us adults?

75
00:04:12,910 --> 00:04:13,999
Right.

76
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,749
A neighbor's kid of mine

77
00:04:15,750 --> 00:04:17,189
had a fight with his mother once

78
00:04:17,190 --> 00:04:18,359
and ran away from home.

79
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,189
They called the police.

80
00:04:19,190 --> 00:04:20,879
Everyone searched for three whole days.

81
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:22,749
Finally, his grandmother remembered

82
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:24,479
that the kid used to
run to the pigeon coop

83
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:26,069
on the neighbor's roof.

84
00:04:26,070 --> 00:04:27,559
The family was worried sick,

85
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,269
but the kid was right under their noses.

86
00:04:29,270 --> 00:04:31,120
eating and sleeping just fine.

87
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,599
In that case,

88
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:34,800
let's all do some brainstorming.

89
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:37,150
We can't do anything else
right now anyway.

90
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:52,200
You're awake, Yongjiu?

91
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:56,470
How is she?

92
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:58,920
She just fell asleep.

93
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:01,240
What did the doctor say?

94
00:05:02,630 --> 00:05:04,749
Her immunity has dropped

95
00:05:04,750 --> 00:05:06,239
due to long-term stress.

96
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,439
Her white blood cell count

97
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:09,270
has also increased significantly.

98
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:11,630
There are still many tests to be done.

99
00:05:13,440 --> 00:05:15,359
You don't look well either, Yongjiu.

100
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,799
Go back and rest for a bit.

101
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:18,070
Get some sleep.

102
00:05:18,750 --> 00:05:19,800
Forget it.

103
00:05:19,830 --> 00:05:22,030
Fei hasn't been found,
and now Jing is sick.

104
00:05:22,190 --> 00:05:23,560
I'm in no mood for that.

105
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:26,440
That won't do. You have to sleep.

106
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,149
If Jing has collapsed,

107
00:05:28,150 --> 00:05:29,509
you must hold it together.

108
00:05:29,510 --> 00:05:31,800
Someone needs to be there
to care for Fei.

109
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:32,879
Right.

110
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:33,919
Since you're here,

111
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,269
please keep an eye on her for me.

112
00:05:35,270 --> 00:05:36,679
I'm going back to the shop.

113
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:38,599
I had the kitchen
make some chicken soup.

114
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,879
I'll go back and get it

115
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:41,479
so she can have some
when she wakes up.

116
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:42,510
Okay.

117
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,030
I'm counting on you.

118
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:46,120
Yongjiu...

119
00:05:46,830 --> 00:05:47,799
Well,

120
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:48,599
I wanted to ask

121
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:50,709
if there is any food Fei loves

122
00:05:50,710 --> 00:05:51,999
but is usually restricted from

123
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:54,000
having too often?

124
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,309
That would be

125
00:05:56,310 --> 00:05:58,240
the spicy chicken burger meal.

126
00:05:58,480 --> 00:06:00,629
Fei gets a nosebleed
every time she has it,

127
00:06:00,630 --> 00:06:03,440
so Shu Jing strictly controls it.

128
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,949
She only has it

129
00:06:04,950 --> 00:06:06,440
once every month or two.

130
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,240
Why are you asking?

131
00:06:08,390 --> 00:06:09,829
Xiezhi asked for it.

132
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:11,709
We're just brainstorming

133
00:06:11,710 --> 00:06:12,599
to see if there's

134
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:14,920
any chance Fei might have
gone elsewhere.

135
00:06:15,070 --> 00:06:16,599
Go back and get some sleep, Yongjiu.

136
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,239
Alright.

137
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,629
I'll keep you posted.

138
00:06:18,630 --> 00:06:19,630
Okay.

139
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:29,150
Chicken burger meal.

140
00:06:29,710 --> 00:06:31,200
(So many shops...)

141
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:34,070
(This is where she went missing.)

142
00:06:39,390 --> 00:06:40,680
Judge Shen.

143
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:43,030
I just met a client here.

144
00:06:43,070 --> 00:06:44,950
I turned around and happened to see you.

145
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:49,120
Regarding the hearing
for my client, Ms. Ding,

146
00:06:49,190 --> 00:06:51,680
could you please
adjust the time for me?

147
00:06:51,950 --> 00:06:53,590
No other time works.

148
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:57,599
You can't send me private messages
whenever you want.

149
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,439
Especially messages

150
00:06:58,440 --> 00:07:00,800
that disrupt my professional rhythm.

151
00:07:02,070 --> 00:07:03,239
No.

152
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,439
I wouldn't dare.

153
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:06,359
I'd never interfere with your work.

154
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:08,440
It was merely a request.

155
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,070
A humble request.

156
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,559
Could the hearing

157
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:14,189
be moved forward just a little?

158
00:07:14,190 --> 00:07:15,269
But the exact time

159
00:07:15,270 --> 00:07:17,200
is entirely up to you.

160
00:07:17,270 --> 00:07:18,189
Right?

161
00:07:18,190 --> 00:07:19,390
It's not possible.

162
00:07:20,070 --> 00:07:21,269
No extensions,

163
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:22,680
and no moving it up.

164
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:29,240
Master, let's eat some dinner first.

165
00:07:30,270 --> 00:07:31,799
Has Tong been found?

166
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,030
Not yet.

167
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:37,950
Goodness, Jing's family has
really been through a lot.

168
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,709
They only meant well
when they took care of Tong.

169
00:07:40,710 --> 00:07:43,200
They hoped Tong could
move past this soon.

170
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:47,439
Master, please eat first.

171
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,629
I don't have time to eat.

172
00:07:48,630 --> 00:07:50,239
I have to get this done by morning.

173
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:52,710
It won't take long. Just eat.

174
00:07:55,510 --> 00:07:57,120
I'm going to look for Fei.

175
00:07:57,270 --> 00:07:58,919
Judge Shen, let me help you.

176
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:00,239
The search is a personal matter.

177
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,590
It's not official business.

178
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:05,360
A judge of the people serves the people.

179
00:08:06,440 --> 00:08:08,359
Chief Judge Shu upheld justice

180
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:09,829
and has suffered retaliation.

181
00:08:09,830 --> 00:08:12,479
As a member of the public,

182
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:14,119
if I have any conscience at all,

183
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:16,360
I must do my part to help.

184
00:08:18,070 --> 00:08:19,710
I don't expect anything in return.

185
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:22,920
I appreciate your enthusiasm
and conscience.

186
00:08:23,150 --> 00:08:24,799
A judge must maintain their integrity.

187
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:26,629
They don't take from the public,

188
00:08:26,630 --> 00:08:29,359
so I certainly can't use your free labor.

189
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,709
You should just go home.

190
00:08:30,710 --> 00:08:32,359
You're heading
to burger shops, aren't you?

191
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:34,029
There are hundreds of them
in Tianhai City.

192
00:08:34,030 --> 00:08:35,959
Even more if you count
the fried chicken places.

193
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,590
You need help.

194
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:41,079
I don't plan on searching aimlessly.

195
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,909
I'm not saying your plan is flawed.

196
00:08:42,910 --> 00:08:43,629
I'm just saying

197
00:08:43,630 --> 00:08:46,200
we should tweak it slightly.

198
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:48,669
Tong and Fei are just kids,

199
00:08:48,670 --> 00:08:49,549
but this is still

200
00:08:49,550 --> 00:08:51,199
a case of kidnapping.

201
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,549
They don't necessarily need burgers.

202
00:08:52,550 --> 00:08:53,959
A box of instant noodles

203
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,350
would solve their problem.

204
00:08:56,030 --> 00:08:57,440
By your logic,

205
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:59,830
there are over ten thousand locations,

206
00:08:59,880 --> 00:09:01,509
including supermarkets
and convenience stores.

207
00:09:01,510 --> 00:09:02,640
How do we find them?

208
00:09:06,030 --> 00:09:07,160
Judge Shen.

209
00:09:07,270 --> 00:09:09,269
Judge Shen, that's not what I meant.

210
00:09:09,270 --> 00:09:10,750
What I mean is,

211
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:11,749
food is a priority,

212
00:09:11,750 --> 00:09:13,509
but shelter is also a basic need.

213
00:09:13,510 --> 00:09:14,839
They have no adult with them.

214
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:17,070
Where would two little girls stay?

215
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:18,269
Do you think

216
00:09:18,270 --> 00:09:19,990
the police haven't thought of that?

217
00:09:20,390 --> 00:09:22,119
Right. Checking surveillance,

218
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:24,119
sending notices to hotels, guesthouses,

219
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:25,199
and residential areas...

220
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,879
They're definitely doing all that.

221
00:09:26,880 --> 00:09:27,879
My point is,

222
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:28,909
is it possible

223
00:09:28,910 --> 00:09:31,359
to check Tong's social circle?

224
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:33,079
Look into her close friends.

225
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:36,400
Maybe someone has an empty house
or a villa or something.

226
00:09:36,630 --> 00:09:38,680
The police would have
thought of that too.

227
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:40,879
But if they're actually helping Tong,

228
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:42,509
they certainly won't tell the truth

229
00:09:42,510 --> 00:09:43,800
to parents or the police.

230
00:09:43,910 --> 00:09:46,520
Then, why would they
be honest with us?

231
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:51,879
In that case,

232
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:52,879
does Tong really have

233
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:54,750
a friend she's that close to?

234
00:09:55,270 --> 00:09:57,079
Is there anyone whose family is so rich

235
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:59,160
that they have houses
they've forgotten about?

236
00:10:00,150 --> 00:10:02,509
Or maybe someone
with a factory in the suburbs?

237
00:10:02,510 --> 00:10:03,839
With rows and rows of warehouses

238
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:05,320
that no one ever checks.

239
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:08,029
Or even

240
00:10:08,030 --> 00:10:10,719
someone who owns
a fried chicken chain?

241
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:11,509
If those two kids

242
00:10:11,510 --> 00:10:13,479
hid in a food warehouse,

243
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:15,719
they could just grab fast food

244
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:17,800
when the staff isn't looking.

245
00:10:18,790 --> 00:10:19,950
I'm tired.

246
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,479
Go back and get some rest.

247
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:23,640
Eat something
and give your brain a rest.

248
00:10:23,910 --> 00:10:24,990
I'm not tired.

249
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:26,750
I really just want to help.

250
00:10:32,160 --> 00:10:33,600
(Xianghui)

251
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:36,719
Hello, Xianghui.

252
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:37,669
Judge Shen.

253
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:39,359
I just called Tong's mom.

254
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:42,429
She said Tong has a friend
she often plays with named Xiaohu.

255
00:10:42,430 --> 00:10:44,999
His family runs a food additive factory.

256
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:47,549
They have a house
in the East Lake Scenic Area

257
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:49,280
that's currently being
used as a guesthouse.

258
00:10:49,390 --> 00:10:51,920
There are quite a few small inns nearby.

259
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:54,389
They might not strictly
enforce guest registration.

260
00:10:54,390 --> 00:10:56,239
Hu Aixi and I are heading over there

261
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:57,920
to ask around and check things out.

262
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,199
If it's convenient for you,

263
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:01,119
could you go take a look at his factory?

264
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:03,070
It's in the Economic Development Zone.

265
00:11:03,390 --> 00:11:05,830
It's about a thirty-minute drive.

266
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:06,719
Alright.

267
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,749
Send me the address.

268
00:11:07,750 --> 00:11:08,839
I'm heading there now.

269
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:09,800
Okay.

270
00:11:10,880 --> 00:11:12,440
We have a new lead.

271
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:17,599
A villa...

272
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:19,560
A food additive factory...

273
00:11:19,910 --> 00:11:21,710
I was right!

274
00:11:22,430 --> 00:11:22,999
Let's go.

275
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,999
Let's hurry and find the kids.

276
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,039
Call a ride, quickly.

277
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:28,960
(Tianhai City Food Additive Factory)

278
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:32,040
Wait.

279
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,710
What are you dilly-dallying for?

280
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:36,200
Let's go.

281
00:11:39,910 --> 00:11:42,470
Are you still considering
whether or not to take me?

282
00:11:45,550 --> 00:11:46,920
Judge Shen,

283
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:48,549
trust me.

284
00:11:48,550 --> 00:11:49,999
With my IQ,

285
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:52,040
I'll definitely be of help to you.

286
00:12:00,510 --> 00:12:01,830
Thanks, sir.

287
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:03,160
Thank you, sir.

288
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,429
Are you scared?

289
00:12:18,430 --> 00:12:20,350
If you are,
it's not too late to back out.

290
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:22,160
Who says I'm scared?

291
00:12:22,550 --> 00:12:24,269
I'm with a people's judge.

292
00:12:24,270 --> 00:12:25,680
What is there to be afraid of?

293
00:12:26,150 --> 00:12:26,629
Besides,

294
00:12:26,630 --> 00:12:28,909
you radiate a strong sense of justice.

295
00:12:28,910 --> 00:12:31,280
Even if the sky falls,
you're here to hold it up.

296
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:37,789
(Tianhai City Food Additive Factory)

297
00:12:37,790 --> 00:12:38,950
Hello?

298
00:12:41,030 --> 00:12:42,230
Is anyone there?

299
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:44,280
Hello?

300
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,590
Who is it?

301
00:12:46,660 --> 00:12:47,719
Who are you looking for?

302
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:48,509
Hello.

303
00:12:48,510 --> 00:12:50,629
I'm from the Qingcheng District
People's Court.

304
00:12:50,630 --> 00:12:52,909
I'd like to ask you a few questions.

305
00:12:52,910 --> 00:12:54,990
What has Fan Xiaohu done this time?

306
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:56,429
You know him?

307
00:12:56,430 --> 00:12:57,830
I'm his uncle.

308
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:00,079
His father is delivering goods
in Inner Mongolia.

309
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:01,549
Just half an hour ago,

310
00:13:01,550 --> 00:13:03,200
the police were here asking questions.

311
00:13:03,270 --> 00:13:05,429
Is this about the same thing?

312
00:13:05,430 --> 00:13:07,429
Is it about a girl named Tong?

313
00:13:07,430 --> 00:13:09,590
I already told the police.

314
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:11,280
They haven't been here.

315
00:13:11,550 --> 00:13:14,239
Xiaohu has been living with his mother
for the past two months.

316
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:15,389
He hasn't come back either.

317
00:13:15,390 --> 00:13:16,560
The police

318
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:18,070
have already looked inside.

319
00:13:22,630 --> 00:13:23,870
Let's go.

320
00:13:34,790 --> 00:13:37,110
(Hotel)
Hello, have you seen this girl?

321
00:13:38,430 --> 00:13:39,590
No.

322
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:40,789
How about this one?

323
00:13:40,790 --> 00:13:41,669
No.

324
00:13:41,670 --> 00:13:42,920
Thank you.

325
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,509
Hello. Have you seen this person?

326
00:13:46,510 --> 00:13:47,079
No.

327
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:49,029
- Hi there. Have you seen her?
- Haven't seen her.

328
00:13:49,030 --> 00:13:49,629
No.

329
00:13:49,630 --> 00:13:50,959
Do you recognize this girl?

330
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:51,789
Have you seen her?

331
00:13:51,790 --> 00:13:52,389
No.

332
00:13:52,390 --> 00:13:53,079
Sorry to trouble you.

333
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:54,199
Have you seen this girl?

334
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:55,590
Have you seen her?

335
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:57,320
No.

336
00:13:58,430 --> 00:13:59,870
Still nothing.

337
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:16,119
Zhengyi.

338
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:17,509
I've arrived at the office.

339
00:14:17,510 --> 00:14:19,029
Finish the pre-trial preparations.

340
00:14:19,030 --> 00:14:20,350
I'll be there in a moment.

341
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:24,479
How is it, Le?

342
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:26,160
How's the situation with Ms. Shu?

343
00:14:26,510 --> 00:14:28,350
She's still running a fever.

344
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,629
When she woke up this morning,

345
00:14:29,630 --> 00:14:31,149
she insisted on being discharged.

346
00:14:31,150 --> 00:14:33,440
The doctor gave Jing an order.

347
00:14:34,030 --> 00:14:35,319
Mandatory rest.

348
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:36,560
What about Fei?

349
00:14:38,630 --> 00:14:40,070
Still no news.

350
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,879
The police have already pulled

351
00:14:41,880 --> 00:14:44,199
all the footage near the theater.

352
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:45,079
But for that performance,

353
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,719
the kids were all dressed so similarly.

354
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:49,440
You can't tell who is who.

355
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:51,800
And the SIM card

356
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:52,669
in Tong's phone

357
00:14:52,670 --> 00:14:54,070
isn't in use anymore.

358
00:14:54,510 --> 00:14:56,629
The kid must have
planned this in advance.

359
00:14:56,630 --> 00:14:59,230
They clearly don't want to
talk to adults anymore.

360
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:02,359
Fei and her friend are so bold.

361
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:04,239
And my heart really goes out to Tong.

362
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:05,239
Why do you think Fei

363
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:07,070
is so unwilling
to talk to her parents?

364
00:15:08,430 --> 00:15:10,429
You wouldn't know
because you haven't raised kids.

365
00:15:10,430 --> 00:15:11,959
Trust between children and parents

366
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:14,560
is actually very easily affected.

367
00:15:15,550 --> 00:15:17,040
Listen to you.

368
00:15:17,150 --> 00:15:18,959
That might be true for ordinary parents.

369
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:20,389
But our Ms. Shu and Mr. Lian

370
00:15:20,390 --> 00:15:21,719
are judges of the people.

371
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:22,909
If she can't trust them,

372
00:15:22,910 --> 00:15:24,470
who can she trust?

373
00:15:24,670 --> 00:15:27,199
Professional image and family roles
are two different things.

374
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:28,950
That's exactly it.

375
00:15:30,630 --> 00:15:32,029
Look at Mr. Ying.

376
00:15:32,030 --> 00:15:34,429
The bedtime stories he tells his son

377
00:15:34,430 --> 00:15:37,079
are all adapted from his current cases.

378
00:15:37,080 --> 00:15:39,199
They're nothing but dark fairy tales.

379
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:40,590
No way.

380
00:15:41,200 --> 00:15:42,509
If you ask me,

381
00:15:42,510 --> 00:15:44,200
being a judge's child

382
00:15:44,510 --> 00:15:46,520
requires great mental strength.

383
00:15:46,910 --> 00:15:48,160
It's just too hard.

384
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:52,839
So,

385
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:53,909
the IV is finished.

386
00:15:53,910 --> 00:15:54,750
Alright.

387
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:01,749
You're awake.

388
00:16:01,750 --> 00:16:03,479
You have another check-up
to do in a bit.

389
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:04,719
Don't forget.

390
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:05,199
Okay.

391
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:06,269
Please press down on this.

392
00:16:06,270 --> 00:16:07,269
Okay.

393
00:16:07,270 --> 00:16:08,479
Alright, thank you for your help.

394
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:09,680
No problem.

395
00:16:11,390 --> 00:16:13,160
Has Fei been found?

396
00:16:14,800 --> 00:16:15,480
Not yet.

397
00:16:17,480 --> 00:16:18,029
You're here.

398
00:16:18,030 --> 00:16:19,200
Yongjiu.

399
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:21,440
You're finally awake.

400
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:24,040
How are you feeling, Jing?

401
00:16:24,150 --> 00:16:24,879
Pretty good.

402
00:16:24,880 --> 00:16:25,719
Do you want to eat?

403
00:16:25,720 --> 00:16:27,359
Look what I brought you today.

404
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:29,359
I should do the check-up first.

405
00:16:29,360 --> 00:16:31,320
Alright, let's do the check-up then.

406
00:16:33,880 --> 00:16:36,160
You look a bit better today.

407
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:37,079
Let's go.

408
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:37,990
Come on.

409
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:45,800
Careful, take it slow.

410
00:16:52,550 --> 00:16:53,719
Okay, let's go.

411
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:54,509
Yongjiu,

412
00:16:54,510 --> 00:16:55,079
give that to me.

413
00:16:55,080 --> 00:16:56,830
I'll take Jing for her check-up.

414
00:16:57,430 --> 00:16:59,149
Eat your food while it's hot.

415
00:16:59,150 --> 00:17:00,029
You have to head back

416
00:17:00,030 --> 00:17:01,509
to the mutton soup shop later.

417
00:17:01,510 --> 00:17:03,389
Alright, I'll leave her in your hands.

418
00:17:03,390 --> 00:17:04,600
Don't mention it.

419
00:17:05,150 --> 00:17:06,200
Let's go.

420
00:17:17,670 --> 00:17:19,279
I don't know if you have

421
00:17:19,280 --> 00:17:22,039
the brain of a master detective,

422
00:17:22,040 --> 00:17:23,680
but you've certainly got the look.

423
00:17:24,920 --> 00:17:25,759
(Driving Route)

424
00:17:25,760 --> 00:17:26,669
I'm looking for

425
00:17:26,670 --> 00:17:29,400
where Fei and Tong might be hiding.

426
00:17:29,670 --> 00:17:30,920
Do you have a lead?

427
00:17:30,990 --> 00:17:33,149
The last footage we have shows

428
00:17:33,150 --> 00:17:34,799
they were traveling on foot.

429
00:17:34,800 --> 00:17:36,669
No one was with them,

430
00:17:36,670 --> 00:17:38,429
and they didn't use any transportation.

431
00:17:38,430 --> 00:17:40,039
Looking at the map,

432
00:17:40,040 --> 00:17:42,310
this area is part
of the old city's renovation zone.

433
00:17:42,670 --> 00:17:44,279
The large residential sections here

434
00:17:44,280 --> 00:17:45,950
have been demolished.

435
00:17:46,150 --> 00:17:46,799
That rules out

436
00:17:46,800 --> 00:17:48,790
them staying at someone's house.

437
00:17:49,080 --> 00:17:51,680
Since they need food and shelter,

438
00:17:51,710 --> 00:17:53,079
this construction site is surrounded

439
00:17:53,080 --> 00:17:55,319
by many workers and street vendors.

440
00:17:55,320 --> 00:17:56,279
It's the most likely place

441
00:17:56,280 --> 00:17:58,389
to find food and water.

442
00:17:58,390 --> 00:17:59,519
Plus, with the recent

443
00:17:59,520 --> 00:18:01,200
continuous rainfall,

444
00:18:01,200 --> 00:18:02,840
(Honglong Plaza)
they would definitely choose

445
00:18:02,840 --> 00:18:04,680
somewhere that provides shelter.

446
00:18:04,710 --> 00:18:06,389
Based on all these factors,

447
00:18:06,390 --> 00:18:07,949
these abandoned malls

448
00:18:07,950 --> 00:18:10,400
are their most likely hiding spots.

449
00:18:19,520 --> 00:18:20,559
Not bad.

450
00:18:20,560 --> 00:18:22,790
Those glasses really make you
look like a detective.

451
00:18:22,990 --> 00:18:25,230
Then, analyze the location for me.

452
00:18:25,470 --> 00:18:27,359
Don't mock me, okay?

453
00:18:27,360 --> 00:18:28,909
This place is hard to find.

454
00:18:28,910 --> 00:18:29,879
It's very specific.

455
00:18:29,880 --> 00:18:31,669
Even though it's in the old city,

456
00:18:31,670 --> 00:18:34,080
it's an abandoned mall.

457
00:18:34,120 --> 00:18:35,909
The two kids would have to find a place

458
00:18:35,910 --> 00:18:37,119
with no surveillance cameras,

459
00:18:37,120 --> 00:18:38,470
no ID required,

460
00:18:38,600 --> 00:18:40,429
and preferably somewhere
sparsely populated,

461
00:18:40,430 --> 00:18:41,759
where few people go.

462
00:18:41,760 --> 00:18:43,120
It also can't be too far.

463
00:18:43,630 --> 00:18:45,909
I think this place

464
00:18:45,910 --> 00:18:47,949
is right here.

465
00:18:47,950 --> 00:18:48,880
(Honglong Plaza)

466
00:18:51,390 --> 00:18:52,640
You're wiping this later.

467
00:18:54,080 --> 00:18:55,189
I know.

468
00:18:55,190 --> 00:18:57,079
Then hurry up
and tell the police your idea.

469
00:18:57,080 --> 00:18:58,510
Let them check it out.

470
00:18:58,710 --> 00:18:59,279
My idea

471
00:18:59,280 --> 00:19:00,629
is just one of

472
00:19:00,630 --> 00:19:01,950
a thousand possibilities.

473
00:19:02,040 --> 00:19:04,079
Besides, I'm no Di Renjie.
[*A famous detective in Tang Dynasty]

474
00:19:04,080 --> 00:19:04,759
I can't mobilize

475
00:19:04,760 --> 00:19:06,389
the entire Court of Judicial Review.

476
00:19:06,390 --> 00:19:08,079
Are you planning to go with Shen Xiezhi

477
00:19:08,080 --> 00:19:11,559
and search this abandoned mall
all by yourselves?

478
00:19:11,560 --> 00:19:12,880
What else?

479
00:19:18,390 --> 00:19:20,319
Are you really going to all this trouble

480
00:19:20,320 --> 00:19:22,950
just for Ms. Ding's case?

481
00:19:23,320 --> 00:19:24,559
What else?

482
00:19:24,560 --> 00:19:28,229
Putting up a front for something else?

483
00:19:28,230 --> 00:19:30,550
Nope, don't get the wrong idea.

484
00:19:30,760 --> 00:19:32,750
He and I are just acquaintances at best.

485
00:19:33,230 --> 00:19:34,470
Just on nodding terms.

486
00:19:35,520 --> 00:19:37,360
Fine, fine, nodding terms.

487
00:19:37,520 --> 00:19:38,640
What?

488
00:19:38,710 --> 00:19:39,880
You don't believe me?

489
00:19:40,280 --> 00:19:41,319
Ms. Ding's case

490
00:19:41,320 --> 00:19:43,310
is worth 20,000 yuan once settled.

491
00:19:43,360 --> 00:19:45,519
That covers several months
of rent and utilities for us.

492
00:19:45,520 --> 00:19:46,510
Fine.

493
00:19:47,360 --> 00:19:48,839
Since you don't care about the money,

494
00:19:48,840 --> 00:19:50,310
then I don't care either.

495
00:19:50,990 --> 00:19:52,799
I don't need to
work on this case anymore.

496
00:19:52,800 --> 00:19:54,200
I might as well just lie flat.

497
00:19:55,040 --> 00:19:56,119
No, no, no!

498
00:19:56,120 --> 00:19:56,599
My lady!

499
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:58,189
I care! Of course I care!

500
00:19:58,190 --> 00:19:59,469
Get up, get up!

501
00:19:59,470 --> 00:20:01,119
I can't support you
for the rest of your life.

502
00:20:01,120 --> 00:20:02,119
Hurry up.

503
00:20:02,120 --> 00:20:03,389
I can't get up. I'm sleepy.

504
00:20:03,390 --> 00:20:04,709
Get up, get up!

505
00:20:04,710 --> 00:20:05,119
Get up!

506
00:20:05,120 --> 00:20:06,990
I can't get up at all.

507
00:20:07,800 --> 00:20:08,989
Then, I'm giving up as well.

508
00:20:08,990 --> 00:20:10,550
I can't support you at all.

509
00:20:17,670 --> 00:20:18,879
What are you all doing here?

510
00:20:18,880 --> 00:20:20,030
Judge Lian.

511
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:23,189
Shu Jing has a check-up.

512
00:20:23,190 --> 00:20:24,990
She'll be back shortly.

513
00:20:27,320 --> 00:20:28,119
Please, have a seat.

514
00:20:28,120 --> 00:20:29,600
Come in, sit down.

515
00:20:31,040 --> 00:20:33,080
- Let me. Thanks.
- No, let me do it.

516
00:20:40,230 --> 00:20:41,359
So, what brings you...

517
00:20:41,360 --> 00:20:42,710
Judge Lian.

518
00:20:43,320 --> 00:20:44,750
I am truly sorry.

519
00:20:45,560 --> 00:20:47,279
I didn't expect Tong to still

520
00:20:47,280 --> 00:20:49,030
be hounding you like this.

521
00:20:49,560 --> 00:20:52,359
You and Judge Shu are such good people.

522
00:20:52,360 --> 00:20:55,120
It's so unfair that you both
have to go through this.

523
00:20:55,950 --> 00:20:58,600
I should have
sent Tong home back then.

524
00:20:59,150 --> 00:21:00,790
This is my debt to her.

525
00:21:01,360 --> 00:21:02,790
Don't worry.

526
00:21:02,950 --> 00:21:05,600
Tong would never hurt Fei.

527
00:21:06,470 --> 00:21:07,559
She really loves Fei.

528
00:21:07,560 --> 00:21:10,160
She treats Fei like her own sister.

529
00:21:10,710 --> 00:21:12,640
Nothing bad will happen.

530
00:21:15,320 --> 00:21:16,669
I've also searched

531
00:21:16,670 --> 00:21:18,230
all the possible places

532
00:21:18,760 --> 00:21:20,270
that we know of.

533
00:21:20,990 --> 00:21:22,429
If Tong wants to hide,

534
00:21:22,430 --> 00:21:24,840
she obviously won't let you find her.

535
00:21:30,430 --> 00:21:32,360
Excuse me, I need to take this.

536
00:21:35,950 --> 00:21:37,360
Hello? Who is this?

537
00:21:37,560 --> 00:21:38,599
It's me.

538
00:21:38,600 --> 00:21:40,230
You should know who I am.

539
00:21:40,710 --> 00:21:41,840
Rapist.

540
00:21:45,990 --> 00:21:47,080
Tong.

541
00:21:47,430 --> 00:21:49,709
Can you tell me where you are?

542
00:21:49,710 --> 00:21:51,149
You won't find us.

543
00:21:51,150 --> 00:21:52,279
Stop looking.

544
00:21:52,280 --> 00:21:54,510
If you want to see Fei again,

545
00:21:54,910 --> 00:21:56,640
you have to turn yourself in.

546
00:21:59,560 --> 00:22:00,759
Judge Lian, let me.

547
00:22:00,760 --> 00:22:01,669
Excuse me.

548
00:22:01,670 --> 00:22:03,030
Tong, it's me.

549
00:22:03,390 --> 00:22:05,310
Do you know what you're doing?

550
00:22:05,520 --> 00:22:06,989
This is a crime.

551
00:22:06,990 --> 00:22:08,759
Stop breaking your mother's heart.

552
00:22:08,760 --> 00:22:09,799
Where are you now?

553
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:11,080
Your mother will go get you.

554
00:22:11,600 --> 00:22:13,120
Li Xueling.

555
00:22:13,280 --> 00:22:14,189
Who are you?

556
00:22:14,190 --> 00:22:15,799
Do you really think you're my dad?

557
00:22:15,800 --> 00:22:17,270
Trying to boss me around?

558
00:22:18,320 --> 00:22:19,550
Tong.

559
00:22:19,670 --> 00:22:21,230
Listen to me, honey.

560
00:22:21,710 --> 00:22:23,799
I can't believe
you're all on the rapist's side.

561
00:22:23,800 --> 00:22:25,079
I'm so disappointed in you.

562
00:22:25,080 --> 00:22:26,880
That's enough, Tong. Stop it.

563
00:22:28,190 --> 00:22:29,270
Wait.

564
00:22:29,280 --> 00:22:30,510
Tong.

565
00:22:30,800 --> 00:22:31,880
Hear me out.

566
00:22:32,040 --> 00:22:33,519
Can we video chat?

567
00:22:33,520 --> 00:22:34,759
Let's talk face-to-face.

568
00:22:34,760 --> 00:22:36,279
I want to confirm
that you're safe, okay?

569
00:22:36,280 --> 00:22:37,920
You rapist!

570
00:22:38,190 --> 00:22:40,039
Stop being so hypocritical.

571
00:22:40,040 --> 00:22:41,079
You can't fool me

572
00:22:41,080 --> 00:22:42,790
with your caring father act!

573
00:22:42,950 --> 00:22:44,759
You only care about work all day.

574
00:22:44,760 --> 00:22:46,879
You don't care
about Fei's feelings at all.

575
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:49,680
I'm the only one
who truly cares for her.

576
00:22:50,080 --> 00:22:51,519
I see it very clearly.

577
00:22:51,520 --> 00:22:52,469
Without me,

578
00:22:52,470 --> 00:22:54,360
she wasn't happy at all.

579
00:22:54,520 --> 00:22:54,989
Tong.

580
00:22:54,990 --> 00:22:56,559
You don't understand the situation.

581
00:22:56,560 --> 00:22:59,270
Fei has severe separation anxiety.

582
00:22:59,390 --> 00:23:00,519
Being away from home this long

583
00:23:00,520 --> 00:23:01,759
is very bad for her.

584
00:23:01,760 --> 00:23:03,359
If you really care about Fei,

585
00:23:03,360 --> 00:23:04,559
just let her come home.

586
00:23:04,560 --> 00:23:05,079
Okay?

587
00:23:05,080 --> 00:23:05,879
Cut the nonsense!

588
00:23:05,880 --> 00:23:07,229
My terms are simple.

589
00:23:07,230 --> 00:23:08,079
Turn yourself in,

590
00:23:08,080 --> 00:23:09,429
and I'll send Fei home immediately.

591
00:23:09,430 --> 00:23:10,920
It's that simple.

592
00:23:12,840 --> 00:23:13,990
She hung up.

593
00:23:14,520 --> 00:23:15,920
She hung up on me.

594
00:23:16,320 --> 00:23:17,359
She...

595
00:23:17,360 --> 00:23:19,759
Today, I want to go check
Dream Star Amusement Park.

596
00:23:19,760 --> 00:23:21,279
Some kids don't know
their own neighborhood,

597
00:23:21,280 --> 00:23:23,319
but they know their way around
an amusement park.

598
00:23:23,320 --> 00:23:25,229
That place is too remote.

599
00:23:25,230 --> 00:23:26,790
I'll go with you later.

600
00:23:27,670 --> 00:23:28,119
That works.

601
00:23:28,120 --> 00:23:29,039
I'll get ready.

602
00:23:29,040 --> 00:23:29,839
and call you later.

603
00:23:29,840 --> 00:23:30,920
Okay.

604
00:23:35,520 --> 00:23:36,949
(Qin Rui)
(According to my analysis,)

605
00:23:36,950 --> 00:23:38,229
(I believe it's likely that Fei)

606
00:23:38,230 --> 00:23:39,279
(is at the abandoned mall,)

607
00:23:39,280 --> 00:23:40,359
(Honglong Plaza.)

608
00:23:40,360 --> 00:23:41,709
(Let's check it out.)

609
00:23:41,710 --> 00:23:43,709
I'm planning to head
to Honglong Plaza in a bit.

610
00:23:43,710 --> 00:23:44,879
Kids don't usually

611
00:23:44,880 --> 00:23:45,839
run to abandoned malls

612
00:23:45,840 --> 00:23:47,389
unless something is going on, right?

613
00:23:47,390 --> 00:23:48,920
Well, something is going on.

614
00:24:08,840 --> 00:24:09,989
How did you figure out

615
00:24:09,990 --> 00:24:12,080
they might be at Honglong Plaza?

616
00:24:12,560 --> 00:24:14,359
I figured these two kids have no IDs.

617
00:24:14,360 --> 00:24:15,599
If they want food and drink

618
00:24:15,600 --> 00:24:17,750
without being discovered,

619
00:24:17,840 --> 00:24:18,989
it must be somewhere

620
00:24:18,990 --> 00:24:21,710
secluded yet bustling.

621
00:24:21,760 --> 00:24:24,229
Starting from where they went missing,

622
00:24:24,230 --> 00:24:26,600
I'm betting on Honglong Plaza.

623
00:24:26,760 --> 00:24:27,629
And I think,

624
00:24:27,630 --> 00:24:29,759
since you're willing to help me look,

625
00:24:29,760 --> 00:24:32,469
you must agree with me.

626
00:24:32,470 --> 00:24:33,799
I agree with your hypothesis.

627
00:24:33,800 --> 00:24:36,080
Furthermore,
I believe Tong didn't take Fei away

628
00:24:36,280 --> 00:24:37,389
out of revenge,

629
00:24:37,390 --> 00:24:39,079
but rather out of a sense of protection.

630
00:24:39,080 --> 00:24:40,949
Tong still insists

631
00:24:40,950 --> 00:24:43,310
that Mr. Lian harmed her that day.

632
00:24:44,230 --> 00:24:45,440
Let's go.

633
00:25:03,120 --> 00:25:04,149
Fei,

634
00:25:04,150 --> 00:25:05,470
stop crying.

635
00:25:05,560 --> 00:25:06,840
Have something to eat.

636
00:25:07,520 --> 00:25:08,879
Tong,

637
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:10,389
I want to go home.

638
00:25:10,390 --> 00:25:12,599
I miss my mom and dad.

639
00:25:12,600 --> 00:25:13,389
Fei,

640
00:25:13,390 --> 00:25:15,119
did you forget what you promised me?

641
00:25:15,120 --> 00:25:16,879
We were going on an adventure together.

642
00:25:16,880 --> 00:25:18,119
I promise you,

643
00:25:18,120 --> 00:25:20,710
this journey will have the best scenery.

644
00:25:20,880 --> 00:25:21,909
And you know what?

645
00:25:21,910 --> 00:25:24,270
The exciting part has only just begun.

646
00:25:27,230 --> 00:25:28,470
Are you thirsty?

647
00:25:35,880 --> 00:25:37,270
Why are you burning up?

648
00:25:39,520 --> 00:25:40,599
You have a fever.

649
00:25:40,600 --> 00:25:42,080
Why didn't you tell me?

650
00:25:43,320 --> 00:25:45,710
This is the number
she used to call me.

651
00:25:46,280 --> 00:25:46,909
Go check it out.

652
00:25:46,910 --> 00:25:47,950
Okay.

653
00:25:49,080 --> 00:25:50,079
Captain Jiang.

654
00:25:50,080 --> 00:25:50,949
I have an idea.

655
00:25:50,950 --> 00:25:52,279
You should just arrest me.

656
00:25:52,280 --> 00:25:53,389
Put me in handcuffs.

657
00:25:53,390 --> 00:25:54,229
When we leave,

658
00:25:54,230 --> 00:25:55,559
let's have someone take a photo.

659
00:25:55,560 --> 00:25:57,559
Then, we'll post the photo online.

660
00:25:57,560 --> 00:25:58,759
I'll get some friends

661
00:25:58,760 --> 00:26:00,229
to help make it go viral.

662
00:26:00,230 --> 00:26:01,879
As soon as Tong sees that photo,

663
00:26:01,880 --> 00:26:02,759
she'll believe

664
00:26:02,760 --> 00:26:03,759
she has achieved her goal.

665
00:26:03,760 --> 00:26:05,120
They will come back.

666
00:26:05,320 --> 00:26:07,550
Judge Lian, you shouldn't say that.

667
00:26:07,760 --> 00:26:10,469
If news of your arrest spreads online,

668
00:26:10,470 --> 00:26:11,799
no matter how we clarify it later,

669
00:26:11,800 --> 00:26:14,039
you'll never
be able to clear your name.

670
00:26:14,040 --> 00:26:14,839
Look,

671
00:26:14,840 --> 00:26:15,909
who gets arrested

672
00:26:15,910 --> 00:26:17,229
is not for you to decide.

673
00:26:17,230 --> 00:26:19,039
This case hasn't been closed yet.

674
00:26:19,040 --> 00:26:20,429
We still need new evidence.

675
00:26:20,430 --> 00:26:22,039
Judge Lian, you know that

676
00:26:22,040 --> 00:26:22,909
the entire legal system

677
00:26:22,910 --> 00:26:25,030
attached great importance to your case.

678
00:26:25,190 --> 00:26:26,879
If we couldn't prove your innocence,

679
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:28,319
we wouldn't have released you.

680
00:26:28,320 --> 00:26:29,949
Now you want us to arrest you again

681
00:26:29,950 --> 00:26:30,949
and say you're the culprit.

682
00:26:30,950 --> 00:26:32,189
That is absolutely impossible.

683
00:26:32,190 --> 00:26:33,389
But you don't need to worry.

684
00:26:33,390 --> 00:26:34,389
We currently

685
00:26:34,390 --> 00:26:36,149
already have some leads on the children.

686
00:26:36,150 --> 00:26:37,079
Plus, the lead you provided

687
00:26:37,080 --> 00:26:38,629
about the phone number,

688
00:26:38,630 --> 00:26:40,359
we can track the cell towers

689
00:26:40,360 --> 00:26:42,559
and should be able
to locate them quickly.

690
00:26:42,560 --> 00:26:43,750
Yes.

691
00:26:43,990 --> 00:26:44,519
Are you ready?

692
00:26:44,520 --> 00:26:45,600
Ready.

693
00:26:45,950 --> 00:26:47,389
If Tong calls again,

694
00:26:47,390 --> 00:26:49,039
try to keep her calm.

695
00:26:49,040 --> 00:26:50,469
Make sure Fei is safe.

696
00:26:50,470 --> 00:26:51,510
Okay.

697
00:26:52,560 --> 00:26:53,599
As for you,

698
00:26:53,600 --> 00:26:54,799
don't worry too much.

699
00:26:54,800 --> 00:26:55,599
Tonight,

700
00:26:55,600 --> 00:26:56,759
stop searching.

701
00:26:56,760 --> 00:26:58,119
If there's any development,

702
00:26:58,120 --> 00:26:59,319
we will contact you.

703
00:26:59,320 --> 00:27:00,550
I was thinking of

704
00:27:00,710 --> 00:27:03,360
checking near her grandmother's house.

705
00:27:04,190 --> 00:27:05,469
Since her grandmother passed away,

706
00:27:05,470 --> 00:27:07,710
she's been saying
she wanted to live there.

707
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:08,839
I have to go and see.

708
00:27:08,840 --> 00:27:10,600
Alright. Please stay safe.

709
00:27:11,360 --> 00:27:12,039
Judge Lian,

710
00:27:12,040 --> 00:27:13,039
there's another thing.

711
00:27:13,040 --> 00:27:13,909
This way, please.

712
00:27:13,910 --> 00:27:15,160
Alright.

713
00:27:17,430 --> 00:27:19,200
Juan, I'll go with you.

714
00:27:28,600 --> 00:27:29,599
Juan!

715
00:27:29,600 --> 00:27:31,200
What's wrong, Juan?

716
00:28:05,480 --> 00:28:08,640
(Xing's dad)

717
00:28:13,880 --> 00:28:14,990
Uncle.

718
00:28:15,630 --> 00:28:16,880
You have to help me.

719
00:28:17,390 --> 00:28:19,160
Tong, where are you?

720
00:28:19,950 --> 00:28:20,839
Tong.

721
00:28:20,840 --> 00:28:22,839
The police already came to see me today.

722
00:28:22,840 --> 00:28:24,039
Uncle,

723
00:28:24,040 --> 00:28:25,550
promise me you won't call them,

724
00:28:25,600 --> 00:28:26,840
okay?

725
00:28:26,950 --> 00:28:28,599
Xing is my best friend.

726
00:28:28,600 --> 00:28:29,599
When I had trouble before,

727
00:28:29,600 --> 00:28:31,079
only you were willing to listen to me

728
00:28:31,080 --> 00:28:32,279
and believe me.

729
00:28:32,280 --> 00:28:33,989
You're different from other adults.

730
00:28:33,990 --> 00:28:35,840
You must help me this time.

731
00:28:37,600 --> 00:28:39,149
Tong, don't worry.

732
00:28:39,150 --> 00:28:40,470
I won't call the police.

733
00:28:40,630 --> 00:28:42,469
But you have to tell me where you are.

734
00:28:42,470 --> 00:28:43,880
What do you want me to do?

735
00:28:44,880 --> 00:28:46,119
Fei has a fever.

736
00:28:46,120 --> 00:28:47,119
She's burning up.

737
00:28:47,120 --> 00:28:49,160
Can you and Auntie
come and help us?

738
00:28:50,040 --> 00:28:51,920
Xing's mom is away on business.

739
00:28:52,080 --> 00:28:52,909
Look,

740
00:28:52,910 --> 00:28:54,750
tell me the address, and I'll come over.

741
00:28:55,230 --> 00:28:56,400
Uncle,

742
00:28:56,430 --> 00:28:57,949
come by yourself.

743
00:28:57,950 --> 00:28:59,119
Don't call the police.

744
00:28:59,120 --> 00:29:01,119
I promise you I won't call the police.

745
00:29:01,120 --> 00:29:02,550
Tell me the address.

746
00:29:02,630 --> 00:29:04,310
I'm coming over now.

747
00:29:24,080 --> 00:29:25,310
This is the place.

748
00:29:27,150 --> 00:29:28,709
This place is deserted.

749
00:29:28,710 --> 00:29:30,310
Do you think they'll be in here?

750
00:29:31,120 --> 00:29:32,440
Let's go up and check first.

751
00:29:32,910 --> 00:29:33,909
Alright.

752
00:29:33,910 --> 00:29:35,440
Wait here. I need to grab something.

753
00:29:47,360 --> 00:29:47,879
Let's go.

754
00:29:47,880 --> 00:29:48,920
Let's go.

755
00:30:08,240 --> 00:30:11,960
(Liu Juan)

756
00:30:22,520 --> 00:30:25,560
(Xing's dad)

757
00:30:28,700 --> 00:30:29,440
Hello?

758
00:30:29,780 --> 00:30:30,550
Hello?

759
00:30:30,630 --> 00:30:32,030
Where is Tong's mother?

760
00:30:32,040 --> 00:30:32,359
I am...

761
00:30:32,360 --> 00:30:34,680
I'm Tong's stepfather, Li Xueling.

762
00:30:35,960 --> 00:30:37,600
(Liu Juan)

763
00:30:49,600 --> 00:30:50,750
Let's go.

764
00:30:54,470 --> 00:30:55,680
Slow down.

765
00:30:56,910 --> 00:30:58,270
Watch your steps.

766
00:31:00,800 --> 00:31:02,080
There's a door here.

767
00:31:03,950 --> 00:31:05,200
This way.

768
00:31:14,600 --> 00:31:15,840
What's that sound?

769
00:31:20,230 --> 00:31:21,429
This place

770
00:31:21,430 --> 00:31:23,080
is quite secluded.

771
00:31:23,190 --> 00:31:25,230
It'd be easy to hide someone here.

772
00:31:34,320 --> 00:31:36,270
If you're scared,
you should head back.

773
00:31:36,800 --> 00:31:38,750
I'd be scared to go back alone now.

774
00:31:42,150 --> 00:31:43,400
It's fine. Let's go.

775
00:31:47,470 --> 00:31:48,750
Why is she so hot?

776
00:31:48,910 --> 00:31:50,710
We need to get her fever medicine.

777
00:31:53,120 --> 00:31:54,079
Tong,

778
00:31:54,080 --> 00:31:55,559
she has a very high fever now.

779
00:31:55,560 --> 00:31:57,229
We must take her
to the hospital immediately.

780
00:31:57,230 --> 00:31:58,920
No, we can't go.

781
00:31:59,120 --> 00:32:01,189
There are cameras at the hospital.
We'll be seen.

782
00:32:01,190 --> 00:32:01,799
The bad guys

783
00:32:01,800 --> 00:32:03,550
will know where we are.

784
00:32:03,950 --> 00:32:05,759
And I'm not kidnapping her.

785
00:32:05,760 --> 00:32:07,230
I'm saving her.

786
00:32:07,430 --> 00:32:08,359
I cannot let Fei

787
00:32:08,360 --> 00:32:10,230
be taken by the bad guys.

788
00:32:10,800 --> 00:32:12,189
But if we don't take her to the hospital

789
00:32:12,190 --> 00:32:13,519
and the fever continues,

790
00:32:13,520 --> 00:32:15,600
her brain could be damaged.

791
00:32:17,880 --> 00:32:18,949
I checked.

792
00:32:18,950 --> 00:32:20,310
There's a pharmacy nearby.

793
00:32:20,390 --> 00:32:22,310
Fei will be fine
once she takes the medicine.

794
00:32:24,190 --> 00:32:25,319
Tong,

795
00:32:25,320 --> 00:32:27,599
whether we buy medicine
or go to the hospital,

796
00:32:27,600 --> 00:32:28,279
we must

797
00:32:28,280 --> 00:32:30,149
take Fei away from here immediately.

798
00:32:30,150 --> 00:32:30,759
This place

799
00:32:30,760 --> 00:32:32,790
will only make her condition worse.

800
00:32:35,150 --> 00:32:36,510
Come on, Fei.

801
00:32:38,150 --> 00:32:39,310
Come.

802
00:32:39,760 --> 00:32:40,229
Okay.

803
00:32:40,230 --> 00:32:41,680
Come on.

804
00:32:59,630 --> 00:33:02,600
Did you hear a sound just now?

805
00:33:03,470 --> 00:33:05,400
I think I heard it too.

806
00:33:06,910 --> 00:33:08,629
This place is so eerie.

807
00:33:08,630 --> 00:33:11,200
Could those two kids
really be hiding here?

808
00:33:24,800 --> 00:33:26,680
There's a car. Let's go.

809
00:33:33,080 --> 00:33:34,470
Let's go take a look.

810
00:33:36,800 --> 00:33:38,510
This way. Come on.

811
00:33:39,840 --> 00:33:41,640
What is it? Careful.

812
00:33:43,080 --> 00:33:44,440
Are you okay?

813
00:33:47,080 --> 00:33:48,949
My head just hurts a little.

814
00:33:48,950 --> 00:33:50,840
There's a thumbtack stuck in your head.

815
00:33:51,670 --> 00:33:52,559
A thumbtack?

816
00:33:52,560 --> 00:33:53,750
Don't touch it.

817
00:33:55,950 --> 00:33:57,149
Will I be disfigured?

818
00:33:57,150 --> 00:33:59,229
We need to treat it fast. Let's go.

819
00:33:59,230 --> 00:34:01,080
Let's go. Don't touch it.

820
00:34:04,240 --> 00:34:04,949
(Clinic)

821
00:34:04,950 --> 00:34:06,120
Stop the car.

822
00:34:07,360 --> 00:34:09,159
You're taking Fei to the hospital
and the police.

823
00:34:09,160 --> 00:34:10,480
You plan to betray me.

824
00:34:12,160 --> 00:34:13,390
Tong,

825
00:34:13,430 --> 00:34:14,759
why don't you trust me?

826
00:34:14,760 --> 00:34:16,520
Hospitals use real-name
registration now.

827
00:34:16,720 --> 00:34:18,109
If you take Fei to the hospital,

828
00:34:18,110 --> 00:34:19,719
the police will find out immediately.

829
00:34:19,720 --> 00:34:21,600
I won't call the police.

830
00:34:22,470 --> 00:34:23,759
I've made you a promise.

831
00:34:23,760 --> 00:34:25,270
Why would I lie to you?

832
00:34:26,720 --> 00:34:27,989
But look at Fei.

833
00:34:27,990 --> 00:34:30,000
She is burning up.

834
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:32,000
Tong,

835
00:34:32,070 --> 00:34:33,680
I remember you said

836
00:34:33,880 --> 00:34:35,270
that Xing's mom and I

837
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:36,679
are the adults you trust the most.

838
00:34:36,680 --> 00:34:38,429
Why should I trust you adults?

839
00:34:38,430 --> 00:34:40,029
But our top priority now

840
00:34:40,030 --> 00:34:42,120
is to take Fei to see a doctor.

841
00:34:42,240 --> 00:34:43,710
If something happens to her,

842
00:34:43,760 --> 00:34:45,430
it will be disastrous.

843
00:34:46,760 --> 00:34:48,029
Look.

844
00:34:48,030 --> 00:34:49,319
Just wait here.

845
00:34:49,320 --> 00:34:50,279
I'll take Fei to a doctor

846
00:34:50,280 --> 00:34:51,600
and be right back.

847
00:35:02,550 --> 00:35:03,680
Fei.

848
00:35:06,030 --> 00:35:08,310
Fei, let's go to the hospital, okay?

849
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:11,389
Fei, trust me.

850
00:35:11,390 --> 00:35:12,839
I am a good guy.

851
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:14,480
Go to the hospital with me, okay?

852
00:35:15,470 --> 00:35:16,600
This...

853
00:35:21,360 --> 00:35:22,480
Alright then.

854
00:35:22,760 --> 00:35:24,029
Let's go to the pharmacy first

855
00:35:24,030 --> 00:35:25,600
to get her some fever medicine.

856
00:35:25,720 --> 00:35:27,759
If the fever still doesn't come down,

857
00:35:27,760 --> 00:35:29,270
we'll take her to the hospital.

858
00:35:33,680 --> 00:35:35,710
It's okay, don't be afraid.

859
00:35:40,990 --> 00:35:42,230
Tong,

860
00:35:43,550 --> 00:35:44,790
I understand.

861
00:35:47,110 --> 00:35:49,430
You once suffered
at the hands of adults,

862
00:35:49,950 --> 00:35:51,879
but the crimes they committed

863
00:35:51,880 --> 00:35:53,159
aren't yours to bear.

864
00:35:53,160 --> 00:35:54,870
This isn't your fault.

865
00:35:55,320 --> 00:35:57,069
It's us adults

866
00:35:57,070 --> 00:35:58,710
who let you down.

867
00:36:07,880 --> 00:36:09,949
I think we should
head to the hospital in a bit

868
00:36:09,950 --> 00:36:11,159
to get you checked out.

869
00:36:11,160 --> 00:36:12,239
He's right.

870
00:36:12,240 --> 00:36:13,279
Although it's a surface wound,

871
00:36:13,280 --> 00:36:15,230
I'd also suggest a tetanus shot.

872
00:36:15,320 --> 00:36:17,270
Don't move. I'll treat it.

873
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:19,549
Doctor, will this leave a scar?

874
00:36:19,550 --> 00:36:20,679
Don't worry, it won't.

875
00:36:20,680 --> 00:36:21,509
Is anyone there?

876
00:36:21,510 --> 00:36:22,239
Yes!

877
00:36:22,240 --> 00:36:23,359
Just a moment.

878
00:36:23,360 --> 00:36:24,279
Wang!

879
00:36:24,280 --> 00:36:25,639
Wang?

880
00:36:25,640 --> 00:36:26,799
Come help with this.

881
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:27,839
Coming!

882
00:36:27,840 --> 00:36:29,029
I'll head over there.

883
00:36:29,030 --> 00:36:30,270
No problem.

884
00:36:33,320 --> 00:36:34,589
Hello, what can I get for you?

885
00:36:34,590 --> 00:36:36,029
Please give me some ibuprofen,

886
00:36:36,030 --> 00:36:37,389
the kind for children.

887
00:36:37,390 --> 00:36:39,200
And some fever patches.

888
00:36:39,470 --> 00:36:40,639
And a thermometer.

889
00:36:40,640 --> 00:36:42,230
Sure thing. Please wait a moment.

890
00:36:43,590 --> 00:36:44,870
Wait.

891
00:36:47,510 --> 00:36:48,870
How old is your child?

892
00:36:49,550 --> 00:36:51,029
He just started primary school.

893
00:36:51,030 --> 00:36:52,879
Take 8ml of this each time.

894
00:36:52,880 --> 00:36:54,389
Four to six hours apart.

895
00:36:54,390 --> 00:36:56,279
No more than four times a day.

896
00:36:56,280 --> 00:36:57,480
Alright, no problem.

897
00:37:02,590 --> 00:37:03,319
Mr. Fang.

898
00:37:03,320 --> 00:37:04,480
What a coincidence.

899
00:37:05,430 --> 00:37:06,589
Judge Shen.

900
00:37:06,590 --> 00:37:07,389
Are you here

901
00:37:07,390 --> 00:37:08,589
to buy medicine too?

902
00:37:08,590 --> 00:37:09,639
No.

903
00:37:09,640 --> 00:37:11,910
A friend got injured,
so we came to get it treated.

904
00:37:15,030 --> 00:37:16,000
Is your child sick?

905
00:37:17,280 --> 00:37:18,350
Yes.

906
00:37:20,990 --> 00:37:22,430
That's 85 yuan in total.

907
00:37:23,030 --> 00:37:23,279
Okay.

908
00:37:23,280 --> 00:37:24,080
I'll scan your code.

909
00:37:25,550 --> 00:37:26,359
Alright, thank you.

910
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:27,319
No problem.

911
00:37:27,320 --> 00:37:28,029
Judge Shen,

912
00:37:28,030 --> 00:37:28,839
I'll head back first.

913
00:37:28,840 --> 00:37:29,799
My child needs the medicine.

914
00:37:29,800 --> 00:37:30,279
Okay.

915
00:37:30,280 --> 00:37:31,199
Okay, goodbye.

916
00:37:31,200 --> 00:37:32,350
Goodbye.

917
00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:33,989
How's it going over there?

918
00:37:33,990 --> 00:37:34,719
I'll pay for this.

919
00:37:34,720 --> 00:37:36,520
Sure, let me check the total.

920
00:37:55,160 --> 00:37:56,549
That's 123 yuan in total.

921
00:37:56,550 --> 00:37:57,680
Okay.

922
00:37:59,720 --> 00:38:01,160
I'm done.

923
00:38:03,590 --> 00:38:05,069
Hurry and get a tetanus shot.

924
00:38:05,070 --> 00:38:06,159
Okay.

925
00:38:06,160 --> 00:38:07,069
Sure.

926
00:38:07,070 --> 00:38:08,270
Let's go.

927
00:38:08,510 --> 00:38:09,279
Don't let it get wet.

928
00:38:09,280 --> 00:38:10,350
Okay.

929
00:38:14,430 --> 00:38:16,040
Did you run into someone you know?

930
00:38:16,110 --> 00:38:17,200
Yes.

931
00:38:17,360 --> 00:38:19,390
A witness from a case
I handled a year ago.

932
00:38:19,430 --> 00:38:20,870
I oversaw it back then.

933
00:38:20,990 --> 00:38:22,390
Let's head to the hospital.

934
00:38:25,590 --> 00:38:26,830
These thumbtacks

935
00:38:27,240 --> 00:38:29,200
are the same
as the one on my head.

936
00:38:30,240 --> 00:38:31,680
What are the odds?

937
00:38:54,200 --> 00:38:54,989
Drink some water.

938
00:38:54,990 --> 00:38:56,310
Thank you.

939
00:38:59,990 --> 00:39:01,230
Fei,

940
00:39:01,800 --> 00:39:03,200
do you feel any better?

941
00:39:06,590 --> 00:39:07,469
Uncle,

942
00:39:07,470 --> 00:39:09,230
you also have a mole on your neck.

943
00:39:24,720 --> 00:39:25,960
Alright then.

944
00:39:26,430 --> 00:39:27,799
You two sleep here tonight.

945
00:39:27,800 --> 00:39:28,909
Early tomorrow morning,

946
00:39:28,910 --> 00:39:30,319
I'll bring some food over.

947
00:39:30,320 --> 00:39:31,870
Call me if anything happens.

948
00:39:32,550 --> 00:39:33,589
Fei,

949
00:39:33,590 --> 00:39:34,870
bye-bye.

950
00:39:48,840 --> 00:39:51,480
(Shen Xiezhi)

951
00:39:52,740 --> 00:39:53,909
Hello, Shen.

952
00:39:53,910 --> 00:39:54,469
Mr. Lian.

953
00:39:54,470 --> 00:39:55,509
How old is Tong's friend?

954
00:39:55,510 --> 00:39:57,230
The second child in Xing's family?

955
00:39:57,390 --> 00:39:58,750
You mean

956
00:39:58,910 --> 00:40:00,790
Tong's classmate,

957
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:02,080
Xing?

958
00:40:02,640 --> 00:40:04,389
They only have one child.

959
00:40:04,390 --> 00:40:05,830
I've never heard of a second one.

960
00:40:06,510 --> 00:40:07,600
Alright, Mr. Lian.

961
00:40:07,640 --> 00:40:08,790
I understand.

962
00:40:10,640 --> 00:40:13,560
(Liu Juan)

963
00:40:26,220 --> 00:40:27,080
Hello?

964
00:40:27,370 --> 00:40:28,180
Hello?

965
00:40:28,360 --> 00:40:29,549
Where is Tong's mother?

966
00:40:29,550 --> 00:40:31,239
She was quite emotional just now.

967
00:40:31,240 --> 00:40:32,910
She is at the hospital now.

968
00:40:33,070 --> 00:40:34,960
Just tell me if there's anything.

969
00:40:36,280 --> 00:40:37,549
I'll send you a location.

970
00:40:37,550 --> 00:40:38,759
Tong is here with me.

971
00:40:38,760 --> 00:40:39,949
I tried my best to persuade her,

972
00:40:39,950 --> 00:40:41,560
but she refused to go home.

973
00:40:42,030 --> 00:40:43,710
I'll find a way to stall her.

974
00:40:44,110 --> 00:40:46,040
Pick her up as soon as possible.

975
00:40:46,430 --> 00:40:48,160
Alright, I'm heading there now.

976
00:40:54,920 --> 00:40:57,200
(Honglong Plaza)

977
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:01,679
Xing's dad is something else.

978
00:41:01,680 --> 00:41:03,750
Knowing Tong was there
but not telling us.

979
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:05,520
Maybe it's because he kept his word.

980
00:41:05,840 --> 00:41:07,750
Tong doesn't even trust her own mother,

981
00:41:07,880 --> 00:41:09,960
yet she was willing
to ask Xing's dad for help.

982
00:41:10,110 --> 00:41:11,279
She must feel that Xing's dad

983
00:41:11,280 --> 00:41:12,870
is a trustworthy person.

984
00:41:13,640 --> 00:41:15,430
Being given such high expectations,

985
00:41:15,510 --> 00:41:17,430
he couldn't break his promise to her.

986
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:19,910
I understand what you're saying.

987
00:41:20,110 --> 00:41:21,199
But this is serious.

988
00:41:21,200 --> 00:41:22,199
For something this big,

989
00:41:22,200 --> 00:41:23,589
if you don't tell the parents,

990
00:41:23,590 --> 00:41:24,319
people will be

991
00:41:24,320 --> 00:41:26,040
worried sick about the girls.

992
00:41:26,110 --> 00:41:27,560
Everyone is getting anxious.

993
00:41:27,950 --> 00:41:29,029
How will Xing's dad

994
00:41:29,030 --> 00:41:31,040
explain himself to Tong's mom later?

995
00:41:32,070 --> 00:41:33,509
Please give me some ibuprofen,

996
00:41:33,510 --> 00:41:34,879
the kind for children.

997
00:41:34,880 --> 00:41:36,279
And some fever patches,

998
00:41:36,280 --> 00:41:37,790
and a thermometer.

999
00:41:38,510 --> 00:41:39,790
Just now,

1000
00:41:40,110 --> 00:41:42,159
Xing's dad bought some fever medicine.

1001
00:41:42,160 --> 00:41:43,639
Fei might be sick.

1002
00:41:43,640 --> 00:41:45,520
We have to find them quickly.

1003
00:41:48,390 --> 00:41:49,870
But that said,

1004
00:41:51,110 --> 00:41:52,199
my little thumbtack

1005
00:41:52,200 --> 00:41:54,750
actually came in handy.

1006
00:42:04,910 --> 00:42:06,270
Let go!

1007
00:42:07,430 --> 00:42:09,200
Let go of me!

1008
00:42:09,990 --> 00:42:11,520
Let go!

1009
00:42:12,470 --> 00:42:13,680
Who's there?

1010
00:42:27,470 --> 00:42:28,680
Who's there?

1011
00:42:42,680 --> 00:42:43,480
(99% Industrial Alcohol)

1012
00:43:14,620 --> 00:43:18,080
♪All the little things
between you and me♪

1013
00:43:18,080 --> 00:43:20,760
♪Woven into our lives♪

1014
00:43:21,610 --> 00:43:23,590
♪The building blocks of life♪

1015
00:43:23,590 --> 00:43:25,290
♪Shape the sky above us♪

1016
00:43:25,290 --> 00:43:27,450
♪Are you doing alright?♪

1017
00:43:27,770 --> 00:43:30,450
♪What are you struggling for?♪

1018
00:43:31,330 --> 00:43:35,150
♪Some questions weigh like mountains♪

1019
00:43:35,530 --> 00:43:40,380
♪How do we piece life back together?♪

1020
00:43:40,940 --> 00:43:45,130
♪So hate can fade
and love feels new again♪

1021
00:43:45,130 --> 00:43:48,200
♪Reclaim the barren parts of life♪

1022
00:43:48,200 --> 00:43:54,570
♪Walking this road
together, still hoping♪

1023
00:43:55,360 --> 00:44:00,420
♪Let me be the wind at dawn♪

1024
00:44:00,720 --> 00:44:04,690
♪Blowing away all the pain♪

1025
00:44:04,920 --> 00:44:09,900
♪Let me be the balance
that holds the weight♪

1026
00:44:10,320 --> 00:44:14,880
♪Where fairness stands♪

1027
00:44:15,350 --> 00:44:17,590
♪Within every heart♪

1028
00:44:17,590 --> 00:44:20,240
♪So many voices calling♪

1029
00:44:20,500 --> 00:44:24,790
♪Struggling, lost,
waiting for an answer♪

1030
00:44:24,790 --> 00:44:27,140
♪Light up the lamps♪

1031
00:44:27,140 --> 00:44:29,810
♪To answer those voices♪

1032
00:44:30,120 --> 00:44:32,240
♪You deserve to be happy♪

1033
00:44:32,240 --> 00:44:34,990
♪Loud and clear♪

1034
00:44:34,990 --> 00:44:37,310
♪All the little things♪

1035
00:44:37,310 --> 00:44:40,010
♪Woven into our lives♪

1036
00:44:40,830 --> 00:44:42,880
♪The building blocks of life♪

1037
00:44:42,880 --> 00:44:44,590
♪Shape the sky above us♪

1038
00:44:44,590 --> 00:44:47,040
♪Are you doing alright?♪

1039
00:44:47,040 --> 00:44:49,150
♪What are you struggling for?♪

1040
00:44:49,400 --> 00:44:51,530
♪Some questions♪

1041
00:44:52,100 --> 00:44:54,800
♪Weigh like mountains♪

1042
00:44:57,690 --> 00:45:02,840
♪Let me be the wind at dawn♪

1043
00:45:03,120 --> 00:45:07,130
♪Blowing away all the pain♪

1044
00:45:07,310 --> 00:45:12,360
♪Let me be the balance
that holds the weight♪

1045
00:45:12,730 --> 00:45:16,430
♪Where fairness stands♪

1046
00:45:16,600 --> 00:45:19,680
♪Within the law♪

1047
00:45:20,840 --> 00:45:29,520
♪And within every heart♪
